### Promenljive okruženja (Environment Variables)
@baseUrl = https://watchlistapi.test/api
@token = 

### ----------------------------------------------------
### 1. AUTENTIFIKACIJA
### ----------------------------------------------------

### Registracija novog korisnika
POST {{baseUrl}}/register
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "name": "Test Korisnik",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

### Prijava (Login) - Kopiraj 'access_token' iz odgovora u @token promenljivu gore
POST {{baseUrl}}/login
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

### ----------------------------------------------------
### 2. WATCHLISTA (Zaštićene rute)
### ----------------------------------------------------

### Dodavanje novog filma u listu (The Matrix)
POST {{baseUrl}}/watchlist
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "imdb_id": "tt0133093",
  "status": "to_watch",
  "rating": 5,
  "personal_notes": "Klasik, moram pogledati ponovo!"
}

###

### Prikaz cele liste filmova (sa paginacijom)
GET {{baseUrl}}/watchlist
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Prikaz liste, ali filtrirano samo za one koje tek treba da gledamo
GET {{baseUrl}}/watchlist?status=to_watch
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Prikaz samo jednog filma (ID = 1 u bazi)
GET {{baseUrl}}/watchlist/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Ažuriranje statusa i ocene filma
PUT {{baseUrl}}/watchlist/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "status": "watched",
  "rating": 4,
  "personal_notes": "Dobar film, ali kraj je malo konfuzan."
}

###

### Brisanje filma iz liste
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/watchlist/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json